# 12.14 Current Limitations

Although the system is functional, several limitations remain.

- Reports are stored in ephemeral container storage.
- No persistent database.
- No authentication.
- No user profiles.
- No conversation memory.
- Sequential tool execution.
- Limited observability.
- No retry policies for tool failures.

These limitations are architectural enhancements rather than functional defects.

