# 12.16 Final Validation Summary

The Study Abroad Finder successfully demonstrates a production-oriented AI agent architecture built on Google ADK and the Model Context Protocol.

Every critical subsystem was validated independently before integration.

The final application successfully combines:

- AI reasoning
- Tool orchestration
- Remote services
- Local services
- Containerization
- Cloud deployment

into a single working system.

This testing strategy provides strong confidence that the implemented architecture is technically sound, reproducible, and suitable as a reference implementation for future MCP-based AI applications.